American based- Nigerian singer, Speed Darlington, has revealed what he would do if harassed for wearing camouflage, in a video posted on his social media page.  Recall we earlier reported that the singer is in Nigeria for Zlatan’s concert. Speed Darlington has not hesitated to express his disappointment in the state of the country since his arrival for his bestie’s concert today.  In a video that has gone viral, Speedy was asked not to wear a camouflaged outfit as the army officers could humiliate him for doing so.  He vowed to beat up any military officer that has the guts to tackle him for wearing the outfit. Speedy revealed that if he was truly humiliated, he would go back to America to expose Nigerians for beating their own citizen.